1
00:00:27,400 --> 00:00:29,719
=Soft-Hearted God=

2
00:00:29,720 --> 00:00:32,099
=Episode 24=
(You collapsed in the snowstorm.)

3
00:00:32,100 --> 00:00:35,957
(My heart turned into a dark shrine.)

4
00:00:43,462 --> 00:00:47,745
(Dexin Hall)

5
00:00:59,580 --> 00:01:01,980
Darn you, heavenly lightning!

6
00:01:04,180 --> 00:01:05,739
Heavenly lightning
doesn't strike mortals.

7
00:01:05,740 --> 00:01:07,339
We can't just stand by.

8
00:01:07,340 --> 00:01:09,900
Everyone,
let's shield Immortal together!

9
00:01:09,980 --> 00:01:10,499
Let's go.

10
00:01:10,500 --> 00:01:10,939
Yeah.

11
00:01:10,940 --> 00:01:11,859
He's right.

12
00:01:11,860 --> 00:01:13,139
We can't just watch him die.

13
00:01:13,140 --> 00:01:15,220
Let's block the lightning!

14
00:01:32,020 --> 00:01:35,219
They once ate immortal flesh to survive,

15
00:01:35,220 --> 00:01:38,300
but now face heavenly lightning
to protect one.

16
00:01:38,340 --> 00:01:41,220
Mortals are truly interesting.

17
00:01:45,180 --> 00:01:47,579
Block the heavenly lightning!

18
00:01:47,580 --> 00:01:48,739
Come at us!

19
00:01:48,740 --> 00:01:51,099
Block the heavenly lightning!

20
00:01:51,100 --> 00:01:53,659
We must protect our savior
even if we die!

21
00:01:53,660 --> 00:01:55,299
We won't let go!

22
00:01:55,300 --> 00:01:57,699
Don't you dare harm our savior!

23
00:01:57,700 --> 00:01:58,979
We can take it!

24
00:01:58,980 --> 00:02:00,540
Come on!

25
00:02:01,820 --> 00:02:02,860
Zhao!

26
00:02:07,100 --> 00:02:08,140
Where's your father?

27
00:02:08,580 --> 00:02:10,340
He's with Xiao.

28
00:02:11,660 --> 00:02:13,459
Come on!

29
00:02:13,460 --> 00:02:14,579
Come at us!

30
00:02:14,580 --> 00:02:15,819
We're not afraid.

31
00:02:15,820 --> 00:02:18,459
We must protect our savior
even if we die!

32
00:02:18,460 --> 00:02:19,620
Zhao!

33
00:02:21,100 --> 00:02:22,859
Heavenly lightning, we're not scared.

34
00:02:22,860 --> 00:02:23,939
Bring it on!

35
00:02:23,940 --> 00:02:25,460
Come at us!

36
00:02:25,660 --> 00:02:26,659
You think we're scared?

37
00:02:26,660 --> 00:02:27,659
We're not afraid!

38
00:02:27,660 --> 00:02:28,700
Come on!

39
00:02:30,820 --> 00:02:31,980
Bring it on!

40
00:02:38,660 --> 00:02:39,899
The lightning stopped!

41
00:02:39,900 --> 00:02:41,260
We won!

42
00:02:43,737 --> 00:02:45,474
♪To meet is to overlap♪

43
00:02:45,475 --> 00:02:47,374
♪To see is to part again♪

44
00:02:47,375 --> 00:02:50,436
♪To stay is to wish for forever♪

45
00:02:50,437 --> 00:02:57,517
♪Counting every moment, unwilling to pause♪
(Qingxin Pavilion)

46
00:02:59,187 --> 00:03:02,859
♪As raindrops kiss the ground♪

47
00:03:02,860 --> 00:03:03,900
Zhao.

48
00:03:05,020 --> 00:03:05,779
Father!

49
00:03:05,780 --> 00:03:06,624
Zhao.

50
00:03:06,625 --> 00:03:11,582
♪Soaking these hazy, drowsy eyes♪

51
00:03:12,775 --> 00:03:14,639
♪Even if reluctant, what can be done♪

52
00:03:14,640 --> 00:03:16,674
♪Chasing something always out of reach♪

53
00:03:16,675 --> 00:03:19,661
♪So I'm afraid of goodbye♪

54
00:03:19,662 --> 00:03:26,000
♪Living the same day
over and over again♪

55
00:03:26,760 --> 00:03:31,080
♪Too bad the rain will stop,
The wind will fade, tomorrow will clear♪

56
00:03:31,087 --> 00:03:33,459
♪I'd rather this night never end♪

57
00:03:33,460 --> 00:03:35,340
What did he do?

58
00:03:35,460 --> 00:03:36,620
Zhao.

59
00:03:37,580 --> 00:03:39,340
What did he do!

60
00:03:39,620 --> 00:03:40,339
He used his powers

61
00:03:40,340 --> 00:03:42,774
to treat all patients
with Verdant Decay.

62
00:03:42,775 --> 00:03:45,536
♪I can hear your voice♪

63
00:03:45,537 --> 00:03:48,486
♪Then let it be our meeting♪

64
00:03:48,487 --> 00:03:50,459
♪Let it be us♪

65
00:03:50,460 --> 00:03:51,620
Zhao,

66
00:03:52,340 --> 00:03:55,300
how could you be so foolish?

67
00:03:57,260 --> 00:03:59,740
I am the princess of Ning.

68
00:04:00,300 --> 00:04:02,179
Saving the people is my duty.

69
00:04:02,180 --> 00:04:03,820
Not yours!

70
00:04:10,020 --> 00:04:11,780
Don't cry.

71
00:04:14,780 --> 00:04:16,620
Stop crying.

72
00:04:17,740 --> 00:04:19,820
Protecting you

73
00:04:20,260 --> 00:04:23,460
has always been my greatest wish.

74
00:04:28,340 --> 00:04:30,340
I don't want your protection.

75
00:04:32,460 --> 00:04:34,740
I don't want it!

76
00:04:35,620 --> 00:04:38,380
I want you alive.

77
00:04:38,580 --> 00:04:40,220
Do you hear me?

78
00:04:40,980 --> 00:04:43,740
I want you alive and well.

79
00:04:45,020 --> 00:04:45,820
I know.

80
00:04:48,620 --> 00:04:50,340
I just want us to be us.

81
00:04:50,900 --> 00:04:53,060
I only want us to be us.

82
00:04:54,140 --> 00:04:55,380
It's useless.

83
00:04:56,940 --> 00:04:58,460
It won't help.

84
00:04:59,260 --> 00:05:00,940
It won't work.

85
00:05:03,820 --> 00:05:06,020
My divine heart is damaged.

86
00:05:06,620 --> 00:05:10,460
This body has lost its foundation.

87
00:05:12,500 --> 00:05:16,020
Nothing can be restored.

88
00:05:18,580 --> 00:05:19,940
They...

89
00:05:20,380 --> 00:05:24,220
helped me block half
(Qingxin Pavilion)

90
00:05:25,700 --> 00:05:27,580
of the heavenly lightning.

91
00:05:28,460 --> 00:05:31,220
Otherwise,

92
00:05:33,460 --> 00:05:35,340
I would've been destroyed.

93
00:05:36,380 --> 00:05:40,220
It turns out mortals
aren't so bad after all.

94
00:05:40,820 --> 00:05:42,060
Xi...

95
00:05:42,260 --> 00:05:43,379
I'm here.

96
00:05:43,380 --> 00:05:44,460
I'm here.

97
00:05:46,140 --> 00:05:48,140
I'm tired.

98
00:05:49,820 --> 00:05:52,260
I want to take a rest.

99
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:05,682
(Qingxin Pavilion)

100
00:06:05,820 --> 00:06:07,580
Zhao!

101
00:06:11,060 --> 00:06:12,900
Zhao.

102
00:06:16,020 --> 00:06:17,460
Zhao.

103
00:06:18,140 --> 00:06:21,245
Zhao!

104
00:06:43,037 --> 00:06:45,620
(One Month Later)

105
00:06:53,162 --> 00:06:55,957
♪Once, the Nine Provinces shone
with brilliant lights♪

106
00:06:56,600 --> 00:06:59,439
♪For you,
I brushed the snow from your robes♪

107
00:06:59,440 --> 00:07:04,882
♪I crossed mountains and seas
just to see you once♪

108
00:07:06,240 --> 00:07:09,679
♪Through countless nights
across rivers and mountains♪

109
00:07:09,680 --> 00:07:13,200
♪Yet we couldn't last through the years♪

110
00:07:13,400 --> 00:07:17,640
♪This parting gathers all joy
and sorrow into silence♪

111
00:07:18,512 --> 00:07:21,799
♪I too once lost myself for ages♪

112
00:07:21,800 --> 00:07:24,799
♪Through love and life, I roamed the mortal world♪

113
00:07:24,800 --> 00:07:31,311
♪Only after a fleeting century
did I learn how shallow this love was♪

114
00:07:31,312 --> 00:07:34,399
♪You're the snow that rests on timeless hills♪

115
00:07:34,400 --> 00:07:36,399
♪You fall into my gaze♪

116
00:07:36,400 --> 00:07:38,399
♪Yet mistaken for the moon♪

117
00:07:38,400 --> 00:07:40,999
♪I break through fate's cocoon♪

118
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:44,840
♪Travel a thousand miles to you♪

119
00:07:44,920 --> 00:07:47,519
♪You are a night of falling petals♪

120
00:07:47,520 --> 00:07:51,920
♪Gone in a blink,
you fade to the horizon♪

121
00:07:51,950 --> 00:07:59,200
♪Telling me not to long for you♪

122
00:08:09,060 --> 00:08:10,140
Your Highness, bad news.

123
00:08:10,180 --> 00:08:11,460
Verdant Decay has reappeared.

124
00:08:12,620 --> 00:08:13,780
What did you say?

125
00:09:02,260 --> 00:09:03,260
(No way.)

126
00:09:03,500 --> 00:09:06,140
(Zhao couldn't possibly
miss out any patient.)

127
00:09:16,500 --> 00:09:17,700
Your Highness, General.

128
00:09:17,900 --> 00:09:19,899
The capital's epidemic
is out of control.

129
00:09:19,900 --> 00:09:21,019
We are in chaos.

130
00:09:21,020 --> 00:09:22,700
Captain Li requests your presence.

131
00:09:28,660 --> 00:09:30,340
Old man of the Heavenly Dao.

132
00:09:30,420 --> 00:09:31,740
Come out!

133
00:09:35,660 --> 00:09:37,540
Old man of the Heavenly Dao!

134
00:09:44,540 --> 00:09:46,060
I hid my form,

135
00:09:46,340 --> 00:09:47,859
yet you still grabbed me.

136
00:09:47,860 --> 00:09:49,859
I want you

137
00:09:49,860 --> 00:09:51,820
destroy that demon root right now!

138
00:09:51,900 --> 00:09:53,340
I can't destroy it.

139
00:09:53,660 --> 00:09:55,460
Only Ye Zhao can do it.

140
00:09:55,660 --> 00:09:57,139
But Father's divine heart is damaged.

141
00:09:57,140 --> 00:09:58,660
He can't destroy the demon root.

142
00:10:00,340 --> 00:10:01,580
Demigod,

143
00:10:01,780 --> 00:10:03,300
let go now,

144
00:10:03,340 --> 00:10:04,820
or I'll get angry.

145
00:10:06,020 --> 00:10:08,460
I'll get angry too if you don't tell me.

146
00:10:09,100 --> 00:10:10,460
Everything in this world

147
00:10:10,620 --> 00:10:12,060
has its reasons.

148
00:10:12,980 --> 00:10:14,539
Arguing with me here

149
00:10:14,540 --> 00:10:15,700
is pointless.

150
00:10:18,780 --> 00:10:19,980
Old man,

151
00:10:20,620 --> 00:10:21,860
you're the best.

152
00:10:22,380 --> 00:10:23,820
Bend the rules a little.

153
00:10:27,380 --> 00:10:29,060
Old man,

154
00:10:29,380 --> 00:10:31,180
please.

155
00:10:37,420 --> 00:10:38,860
I bought this umbrella.

156
00:10:38,980 --> 00:10:40,220
It's yours now.

157
00:10:41,380 --> 00:10:42,540
The snow is heavy.

158
00:10:43,020 --> 00:10:44,460
Go home early.

159
00:10:50,100 --> 00:10:51,300
A divine heart

160
00:10:51,900 --> 00:10:53,580
can only be restored
by another divine heart.

161
00:10:55,660 --> 00:10:57,940
What do you mean?

162
00:11:03,900 --> 00:11:05,019
(Demigod,)

163
00:11:05,020 --> 00:11:06,220
(I hope you'll never)

164
00:11:06,260 --> 00:11:07,820
(have to use this bead.)

165
00:11:11,660 --> 00:11:12,340
After him!

166
00:11:13,860 --> 00:11:14,979
Quick. Over there!

167
00:11:14,980 --> 00:11:16,499
Your Highness, General,

168
00:11:16,500 --> 00:11:17,779
what brought you both here?

169
00:11:17,780 --> 00:11:18,899
What made you ask for us

170
00:11:18,900 --> 00:11:19,940
so urgently?

171
00:11:19,980 --> 00:11:21,660
I never asked for your presence.

172
00:11:23,660 --> 00:11:24,940
You asked for it.

173
00:11:26,540 --> 00:11:27,420
Speak.

174
00:11:28,140 --> 00:11:29,540
Who sent you?

175
00:11:33,740 --> 00:11:35,499
I'm in a terrible mood now.

176
00:11:35,500 --> 00:11:36,940
I have no patience for this.

177
00:11:37,020 --> 00:11:38,420
I'll kill you if you don't talk.

178
00:11:40,140 --> 00:11:41,340
It was Duke Rong!

179
00:11:45,020 --> 00:11:47,820
Is the return of Verdant Decay

180
00:11:47,900 --> 00:11:49,139
his doing?

181
00:11:49,140 --> 00:11:50,019
That day,

182
00:11:50,020 --> 00:11:51,580
the shadow guards were cured

183
00:11:51,740 --> 00:11:53,100
of the Verdant Decay.

184
00:12:01,620 --> 00:12:02,700
Still here.

185
00:12:03,020 --> 00:12:04,220
It's still here.

186
00:12:07,020 --> 00:12:11,220
As long as one Red Spider Lily
still exists,

187
00:12:12,100 --> 00:12:15,420
this plague will never end.

188
00:12:16,100 --> 00:12:17,540
But that flower slave chief

189
00:12:17,780 --> 00:12:20,220
blocked the divine light
meant for His Grace.

190
00:12:20,500 --> 00:12:21,979
Why would he do that?

191
00:12:21,980 --> 00:12:24,619
His Grace heard the chief say

192
00:12:24,620 --> 00:12:25,779
when one has Verdant Decay

193
00:12:25,780 --> 00:12:27,259
and eats Ye Zhao's flesh,

194
00:12:27,260 --> 00:12:29,220
they can turn
into an immortal flower slave.

195
00:12:29,260 --> 00:12:30,899
His Grace wants an army of slower slaves

196
00:12:30,900 --> 00:12:31,779
to rule the world.

197
00:12:31,780 --> 00:12:34,060
Oh no. Zhao is in danger.

198
00:12:34,075 --> 00:12:40,445
(Dexin Hall)

199
00:12:57,062 --> 00:12:58,770
(Qingxin Pavilion)

200
00:13:22,620 --> 00:13:24,379
Master, the immortal body
is as heavy as lead.

201
00:13:24,380 --> 00:13:25,420
I can't lift him.

202
00:13:44,937 --> 00:13:46,646
♪Even if reluctant, what can be done♪

203
00:13:46,647 --> 00:13:49,496
♪Chasing something always out of reach♪

204
00:13:49,497 --> 00:13:52,236
♪So I'm afraid of goodbye♪

205
00:13:52,237 --> 00:13:53,866
♪Living the same day
over and over again♪

206
00:13:53,867 --> 00:13:59,467
(Perhaps, if I reincarnate,)

207
00:13:59,517 --> 00:14:01,116
(I can rid myself of this demon heart.)

208
00:14:01,117 --> 00:14:03,876
(I will definitely
come back to find you.)

209
00:14:03,877 --> 00:14:06,726
(You must wait for me.)

210
00:14:06,727 --> 00:14:09,326
♪If in a dream♪

211
00:14:09,327 --> 00:14:14,116
♪I can hear your voice♪

212
00:14:14,117 --> 00:14:15,876
♪Then let it be our meeting♪

213
00:14:15,877 --> 00:14:18,527
♪Let it be us♪

214
00:14:18,747 --> 00:14:21,466
♪drawing endlessly close♪

215
00:14:21,467 --> 00:14:23,116
♪Too bad the rain will stop♪

216
00:14:23,117 --> 00:14:28,776
♪The wind will fade,
tomorrow will clear♪

217
00:14:28,777 --> 00:14:30,316
♪I can't even hold you properly♪

218
00:14:30,317 --> 00:14:33,066
♪Not even in time♪

219
00:14:33,067 --> 00:14:36,036
♪to tell you how I feel♪

220
00:14:36,037 --> 00:14:38,586
♪If the rain won't stop♪

221
00:14:38,587 --> 00:14:43,226
♪If the wind won't fade,
if time stands still♪

222
00:14:43,227 --> 00:14:45,836
♪Let love go on♪

223
00:14:45,837 --> 00:14:52,947
♪Until forever♪
